title: eBook Collection
description:
Some quality e-books that I do not believe are otherwise readily available online. The PDFs are mostly scans. All books are in English. 

File "File Contents" list the file contents in greater detail than below.

I did not scan the facing pages of Tao teh ching or Tractatus Logico-Philosophicus because the facing pages have foreign languages. The page numbers make it look like every other page is missing, but in each case the entire work in English is included. 

Contains the following:
